    <h1>About SmartPark</h1>
    <p>Welcome to SmartPark — your smart solution for stress-free parking management. Whether you're a casual driver or
        a frequent commuter, SmartPark is designed to help you easily navigate, reserve, and manage parking spaces with
        just a few clicks.</p>
    <p>With SmartPark, you can:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Explore parking lots and spots:</strong> Browse detailed information about available parking
            locations, including real-time availability, spot types, and accessibility options.</li>
        <li><strong>Reserve with confidence:</strong> Book parking spots in advance to secure your place before you
            arrive. Modify or cancel reservations at any time to fit your schedule.</li>
        <li><strong>Manage your reservations:</strong> Keep track of current and upcoming reservations in a clean,
            organized dashboard designed to simplify your day.</li>
        <li><strong>Review your reservation history:</strong> Access a complete history of your past parking activity
            for personal tracking, reimbursements, or business use.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>SmartPark aims to create a seamless and reliable parking experience by combining intuitive design, real-time
        data, and user-friendly tools. Enjoy effortless parking — anytime, anywhere.</p>
